 "title": "Meeting on Kashyyyk",
 "summary": "On the Wookiee homeworld of Kashyyyk, VigCorp's president Twila Delede and her husband Gren are summoned by the Defense Ministry to meet with Luke Skywalker, who arrives in Jedi combat attire amid a Wookiee Honor Guard. After greetings and light banter about the local hospitality and the Wookiees' enduring fondness for Jedi, Skywalker's manner turns somber. He explains that he needs to ask them a question regarding Antoine Dareus, setting a more serious tone for the meeting.",
